 module hotbarautototem
def desc "Auto-totem but just for your hotbar."

on totem_pop if playing {
    if_not hotbar_has #totem {
        input inventory 
        wait 0.05 gui_quickmove #totem 5
        wait 0.05 input inventory
        wait 0.05 swap
    }
}


Swap - swap the item in your main hand to offhand (if not totem , then 😶